{"tid":1378603,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［好Q］劉細良：暫停街頭衝擊，爭取公務員罷工，回歸制度抗爭！","createTime":"2019-07-28T16:14:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T10:44:36.000Z","uid":219007,"like":55,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"5be0e29f4ec8355a9bbc6d5fbd688ea4456ee6e4","tid":1378603,"uid":219007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:14:24.000Z","msg":"細良好Q：<br />\n<br />\n上街示威目的已達到亦應暫停街頭衝擊，現在應團結大多數去支持運動！<br />\n<br />\n我們可向地政總署投訴鄉黑違規再成立民間調查委員會、<br />\n爭取公務員罷工。<br />\n<br />\n有真正獨立調查西環座大廈就會倒塌，這才有一國兩制高度自治！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TfE4DnfVj-Q\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DTfE4DnfVj-Q&d=hFQF9A%2B1epMDho65PkJDL73SwEGp2Am2GayPy7qPUJ4%3D&h=9dc260d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=TfE4DnfVj-Q</a>"},{"pid":"ccd0115a8a734dbe75171258fa112a7c2a4e39ec","tid":1378603,"uid":219007,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:16:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1242a6df51879aa85c6de94081586b0d31bc93a6","tid":1378603,"uid":150625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:25:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dba4188039dcaee4c64bc6ebd8c779ff1afed612","tid":1378603,"uid":14494,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:26:44.000Z","msg":"Why not both?"},{"pid":"522a07ab1d0693e34fa2be4d4ccb2fec2b7ec717","tid":1378603,"uid":266471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:27:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d8fe933ed0c96fc6b4ecd6c77e8a825401ddc47d","tid":1378603,"uid":290385,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:28:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5813461ddd4c4fc45b923ccabc7b470605d6347d","tid":1378603,"uid":289120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:29:10.000Z","msg":"old man push car"},{"pid":"7bf14aa76fca0ca3283303c7b46a6ae86ff180c3","tid":1378603,"uid":225585,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:29:47.000Z","msg":"停你老母<br />\n6月到今日，都堅持兄弟爬山，各有各做，不割席<br />\n<br />\n鄉黑違規係今721先發生？<br />\n一直都有㗎啦<br />\n當年林鄭做政務司時已經想郁鄉黑<br />\n<br />\n要投訴就一早好做啦，等到今日先來抽水<br />\n食屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b171ebe49cede244522376fee3e92eeb62d1783f","tid":1378603,"uid":135867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:29:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"846d00f3dc79e5b2576446642443cbeb224f54f7","tid":1378603,"uid":103353,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:31:51.000Z","msg":"大家記唔記得個loop<br />\n<br />\n和理非-》勇武- 〉和理非"},{"pid":"a605f6c01497993398d4be7d23efa3281a9f83aa","tid":1378603,"uid":39974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:33:39.000Z","msg":"中小規模嘅示威都仲係必需"},{"pid":"3d3e39d0e2296a0b6be84cb0395f29e26b32ba7f","tid":1378603,"uid":79109,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:37:09.000Z","msg":"咪再盲目聽劉細良意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢講政府內部野可能係有料到有道理<br />\n但講抗爭策略就咪亂信啦<br />\n上次講反黑為主題 搞到好似無人提五大訴求咁<br />\n就算要升格 唔該都係真普選<br />\n因為主權不在民 接近無可能搞到班犬<br />\n獨立委員會成立到既機會有幾大？你同我都知<br />\n只有普選，先有可能轉型正義，逐一同班犬計清楚<br />\n<br />\n公務員罷工定集會呢條線根本同上街抗爭係可以共存既，只有用盡一切方法俾壓力個政府，我地先有機贏<br />\n<br />\n制度一早就失效，我地果時就係因為咁先走出黎<br />\n無啦啦咩暫停街頭抗爭？俾班犬好好休息？咪玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f104d5bd67330d36e347f6da6fb6f2f491e0fbac","tid":1378603,"uid":174295,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:38:37.000Z","msg":"幾時有講過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可唔可以放時間出嚟"},{"pid":"6df0ad3bbbafc22f3a